Interface IClassDefinition<D>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanArrayDefinition, ByteArrayDefinition, CharArrayDefinition, ClassDefinition, DoubleArrayDefinition, FloatArrayDefinition, HashMapDefinition, IgnoreDefinition, IntArrayDefinition, LinkedHashMapDefinition, LinkedListDefinition, LinkedListQuickDefinition, LongArrayDefinition, ObjectArrayDefinition, ObjectDefinition, ShortArrayDefinition, StringQuickDefinition

    public interface IClassDefinition<D>
    A Class Definition.

    Defines how to calculate the size of particular object type. Implement definitions for specific types to optimise or correct the basic algorithm.
